msgid ""
"add the IPv6 tunnel IP to Tunnel Address on the WireGuard Local "
"configuration (see further below)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manual/how-tos/wireguard-selective-routing.rst:286
msgid ""
"add :code:`::/0` to the Allowed IPs on the WireGuard Endpoint "
"configuration"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manual/how-tos/wireguard-selective-routing.rst:287
msgid "create an IPv6 gateway (see further below)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manual/how-tos/wireguard-selective-routing.rst:288
msgid ""
"add to the hosts alias the IPv6 addresses of the hosts/networks that are "
"to use the tunnel"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manual/how-tos/wireguard-selective-routing.rst:289
msgid ""
"if necessary, create a separate local IPs alias for IPv6, so they can be "
"excluded from the IPv6 firewall rule destination"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manual/how-tos/wireguard-selective-routing.rst:290
msgid "create an IPv6 firewall rule (specifying the IPv6 gateway in the rule)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manual/how-tos/wireguard-selective-routing.rst:291
msgid ""
"configure an IPv6 floating rule for routing (specifying the IPv6 gateway "
"in the rule)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manual/how-tos/wireguard-selective-routing.rst:292
msgid "create an IPv6 outbound NAT rule"
